nodes.text: Teegu was a female Mahran who was the Secondborn of Ashu, a prominent bloodline of Mahran during the Clone Wars. She was the daughter of Rakshu, her mother, the younger sister of Ashu-Nyamal, and the older sister of Kamu. She had a gift for soothing any squabble. She was killed in space with her family during the mass escape from Mahranee after its attack by Separatist forces.
